UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='I had doubted the possibility of such an item existing. This certainly opens up an incredible opportunity - one we must not squander.$B$BPrepare yourself, $N, for what I am about to ask of you will take you into the depths of hell.' WHERE entry=5461;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='<Leonid looks over the keepsake.>$B$BYour quandary stirs up memories that I had hoped would never resurface.' WHERE entry=5462;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='You place the keepsake on the tainted soil.' WHERE entry=5463;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='As the soul clung to the keepsake, so shall it cling to the physical form of Ras Frostwhisper.' WHERE entry=5464;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='I was certain that you would be joining me as another hapless spirit.' WHERE entry=5465;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Ten thousand souls cry out in unison, $N! You have struck a mortal blow to the Scourge and their masters.' WHERE entry=5466;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='What\'s this? Gloom weed?! I\'ve no need for gloom weed! That mindless mass of flesh is out there picking daisies and convincing the Lady knows how many dupes like you into doing the same. No offense.$B$BVery well, you\'re here now and that\'s all that matters. Since I\'m not going to bother to try to explain things to that abomination how about you collect what I really need... doom weed!' WHERE entry=5481;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Ah, my doom weed. Excellent!$B$B<Junior Apothecary Holland rubs his hands together greedily.>$B$BThese will come in quite handy. You\'ve done me, uh, the Lady, a fine service today $N. As promised here is the reward that you deserve.' WHERE entry=5482;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Ah, goodie!  My bones!$B$BI can\'t wait till the chaps at home see my face on the front cover of Goblin\'preneur.  I\'ll be the richest goblin in the world... and my physical education teacher said I would never amount to anything.' WHERE entry=5501;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='May the spirits bless you, $N. You\'ve done more for Grunth than most would ever think of doing for him. Thank you - you\'re the epitome of what it means to be a hero of the Horde.$B$BPlease - if you can spare the time, come back and visit us. I know that Grunth would like that, as would I.' WHERE entry=5502;
