UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='I am glad you\'ve returned, $N. Some of those loyal to me brought word immediately that the caverns below Orgrimmar were in disarray now that their leaders have been slain. I even heard reports that Neeru was more than agitated. It seems we\'ve put a dent in his armor. I can\'t say I\'m displeased... even with such a minor victory.' WHERE entry=5728;
