UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='A pleasure doin\' business with ya.$B$BAnd $N, wipe that look of disgust off yer face.' WHERE entry=7659;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Are you headed back into the Scholomance, $N? You\'ve already paid such a great price for the use of the Divination Scryer - perhaps you\'d like to take another one with you. With it, you\'d be able to face the perils of the Great Ossuary once more.$B$BBy all means, have it. You\'ve certainly earned it.' WHERE entry=7666;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Your generosity is unrivaled, $N. I thank you for your kindness.$B$BI will be able to finish my divination scryer now, and I should be able to fashion more without further need of diamonds... perhaps you would be interested in helping me in its use? It is for a most important task, I assure you... one that left unchecked could spell unmitigated disaster for the spirit realm!' WHERE entry=7667;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc3='If you bring me your white stallion, I\'ll trade you for one from the new herd. The new horse will be just as fast as your old one, but have a different look to it. You can look at the swift steeds here to see what it will look like.$B$BMUST PAY 500 Gold too....' WHERE entry=7677;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='I never thunk I\'d be lookin\' at thish ugly mug again!$B$BHe acshually looksh better without the resht o\' him attached.$B$BHere\'s yer reward *hic*, $R.' WHERE entry=7701;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Wow... you ARE da true $Gking:queen;! I never think I see this gauntlet in my life! It look like it got no mojo left anymore... maybe that creepy elf try and ruin gauntlet. Well, I say HAR HAR to him!$B$BLook - this mark on da gauntlet an old old OLD timey magic mark, older than da Gordok they say. Well, as Captain of da Gordok, we all learn one thing over and over - how to make mark come to life and give power back to gauntlet!$B$BI do it for you, $Gking:queen;! Here, take da gauntlet and rule FOREVER!' WHERE entry=7703;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='This is better than even I could have thought possible! The Chambermaid\'s magical pillow is mine! You better believe you\'re going to get a nice reward for this accomplishment, $N!' WHERE entry=7704;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Scrumdillyriffic!  These cores will keep me working for some time.  Add to that the benefit of there now being fewer elementals along the coast, and I might no longer cry myself to sleep at the prospect of having set up shop in perhaps the worst place imaginable!$B$BThank you, $N, for your efforts on my behalf.  While it certainly straps me financially to do this, allow me to show you some gratitude you may understand and appreciate... loot!' WHERE entry=7721;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='I hope you kicked his teeth in too, $N. Ragnaros knows, he deserved it.$B$BNow we can get down to business.' WHERE entry=7722;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Ye\'re a good lad, ye are. I got ye a lil\' present fer yer troubles.' WHERE entry=7723;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='<Hansel sneezes.>$B$BI think I\'m gettin\' a cold. Damn this frigid climate!' WHERE entry=7724;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Inconceivably fantastical, $N!  You\'ve come through for me again, and for that I thank you.$B$BThank you!$B$BWhile you may find this coin to be a little less than you\'re accustomed to, rest assured your great deeds on the field of goblindom are echoing through the halls of power in the Steamwheedle Cartel.  Should you need something else to do, then by all means talk to me!' WHERE entry=7725;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Top notch, $N, top notch!  While the coin I give you might not be the most you\'ll ever receive for such work, rest assured my comrades in the Steamwheedle Cartel will hear about your efforts!$B$BIf you are looking for anything else to do, then let me know.  I can always use more elemental cores and such.' WHERE entry=7726;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Oh me achin\' feets.$B$BI figured since ye didn\'t have a luffa...' WHERE entry=7727;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Fantastic work! Now for your reward.' WHERE entry=7728;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='15.9 pounds! That may be a new record for blood and gut weight on apparel! Congratulations, $C!' WHERE entry=7729;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Well done, $C.  Though the extensiveness of the Zukk\'ash presence will not be thwarted with anything less than a full-scale invasion, you have bought us some time so we can devise a proper strategy.$B$BI will be sure to have these carapaces analyzed; we\'ll need to learn everything about them before we deal with what has unfortunately turned into a much larger issue than we had anticipated.' WHERE entry=7730;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Impressive, $C... most impressive!  If Stinglasher is indeed one of their strongest creatures, the study of the beast will prove to be quite valuable in time.  It\'s now my charge to make sure we defend ourselves long enough to take advantage of it.$B$BPlease accept this coin bounty as a token of the entire camp\'s thanks, $N.  Well done.' WHERE entry=7731;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Ah, I\'ve been expecting this.  These creatures you faced... they are an ancient threat that the Horde continues to choose to ignore.  Hadoken was wise to bring this - and you - to me.$B$BThe Zukk\'ash are nothing more than creatures called the silithid.  Some would think that they are a mindless nuisance, but let me assure you - they are a far, far worse threat than anything the Alliance could muster.$B$BIf you\'re willing and strong enough, I could use your aid in bringing this threat to light.' WHERE entry=7732;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Excellent, excellent!  These are going to work out incredibly well - I can already tell that they\'re going to be much harder when properly cured.$B$BThanks again for your help $N.  Here - please take one of my latest creations.' WHERE entry=7733;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Excellent, excellent!  These are going to work out incredibly well - I can already tell that they\'re going to be much harder when properly cured.$B$BThanks again for your aid, $N.  Here - please take one of my latest creations.' WHERE entry=7734;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Incredible!  You may have found the granddaddy of all yeti hides with this!$B$BYou better believe I\'ll pay you for it.  I normally don\'t pay that much for a single hide, but I\'m pretty sure I can make something special from it.  Thanks for thinking of me on this, $N!' WHERE entry=7735;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc3='Let\'s not waste more of my precious time with jibber jabber, $N. It\'s time to focus on replenishing our dwindling fiery flux supply.$BWhat I\'m gonna need from you is the following:$B$B*2 Incendosaur scales.$B*4 Kingsblood.$B*1 Coal.$B$BI\'ll take all that you can offer!$BAnd you\'ll do it fast if you wanna get in good with the Brotherhood.',objectives_loc3='Deliver 2 Incendosaur Scales, 4 Kingsblood and one Coal to Master Smith Burninate.',offerrewardtext_loc3='There\'s always room for more fiery flux, junior. Keep it comin\'... unless I tell you to stop.' WHERE entry=7736;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Keep the residue pouring in!' WHERE entry=7737;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='This is an incredible find! I believe this is the finest yeti hide specimen I have ever seen!$B$BIndeed, this is certainly worthy of an appropriate bounty. I normally don\'t pay that much for a single hide, but I\'m confident I can make something special from it. Thanks for thinking of me on this, $N!' WHERE entry=7738;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='You don\'t even flinch as the smoldering brand is pressed into your flesh. You are so tough!$B$BYou now hold the Mark of Drakkisath. Have fun storming the castle.' WHERE entry=7761;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='You need not be told the meaning of what you have done, $N. This day will be recorded in the annals of history. A victory the likes of which has not been known to the Alliance for years - if ever!' WHERE entry=7781;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='<Field Marshal Afrasiabi bows.>$B$BChoose your reward, let the celebration begin!' WHERE entry=7782;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='You have honored the Horde once more, $N. The son of Deathwing lays dead. Surely, the evil one stirs.' WHERE entry=7783;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Choose your reward so that I may mount the head of the beast for all to see.' WHERE entry=7784;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='May you be protected in your crusade. May the Master bless your efforts.' WHERE entry=7785;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Even in dreams I did not dare foresee this day.$B$BBehold, mortal.$B$BBEHOLD HE WHO IS OLDER THAN EXISTENCE!$B$BBEHOLD HE WHO HAS FACED TITAN AND GOD ALIKE!$B$BRISE MY MASTER! BREAK FROM YOUR BONDS!' WHERE entry=7786;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Please do not harm me! Take it! Take the blade! Leave Demitrian to reshape his pathetic life!' WHERE entry=7787;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='<Captain Shatterskull roars in triumph.>$B$BHow much more can they withstand? How many more Alliance filth must perish at the hands of the Horde for them to retreat? Only time will tell, $R.' WHERE entry=7789;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Wonderful! We thank you for your generous donation, $N!' WHERE entry=7791;
