UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Now isn\'t this interesting? You say you found this tablet on a small, deserted island at The Overlook Cliffs in The Hinterlands, $C? Very interesting indeed. <Oran carefully puts the tablet away and rubs her hands together.>$B$BI thank you for your efforts in this matter. Our Dark Lady shall be very pleased with this discovery. Here, allow me to reward you proportionately.' WHERE entry=8273;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Excellent, a new recruit answering the call to arms against the silithid. Welcome to Cenarion Hold, $C. I am pleased to see the words of our emissaries are reaching heroes of your caliber. You will find no shortage of opportunities to help us in our efforts here and I expect you\'ll quickly prove to be a valuable ally to our cause.' WHERE entry=8275;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Excellent, a new recruit answering the call to arms against the silithid. Welcome to Cenarion Hold, $C. I am pleased to see the words of our emissaries are reaching heroes of your caliber. You will find no shortage of opportunities to help us in our efforts here and I expect you\'ll quickly prove to be a valuable ally to our cause.' WHERE entry=8276;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Cross your fingers, friend!  Here\'s to hoping we can save Noggle!' WHERE entry=8277;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Yes!  It seems to be working, Noggle is coming to.  We owe ya big time!' WHERE entry=8278;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Yes! These are the parts to the book!  Let\'s get started then, $N.$B$BSwap every third word with words from the second chapter... then swap every other word with words from the first chapter...  Wait, did I get that backwards?' WHERE entry=8279;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='You have my sincere gratitude.  Your efforts in helping Cenarion Hold have shown true courage.' WHERE entry=8280;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Excellent!  You\'ve proven to be a valuable ally in preparing for the war against the silithid.' WHERE entry=8281;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Yes!  You brought my satchel back.  And my rare reagents are all here!  I\'ll be in your debt for a long time.' WHERE entry=8282;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Excellent! With Deathclasp gone we\'re free to use the southern mountain range as a strategic path to circumvent the silithid hives. Your work is greatly appreciated.' WHERE entry=8283;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Just as I suspected.  I can decipher individual words in the tablets but they appear to be devoid of any logic or meaning.  It\'s not unknown for Twilight\'s Hammer sects to use a code to hide the meaning of their texts; we\'ll have to go to someone who knows more about this sort of thing.' WHERE entry=8284;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='I see you\'re familiar with my old organization.  You must be with Cenarion Hold.  $B$BYou seek information to use against them?  Come closer, perhaps we can be of mutual assistance.' WHERE entry=8285;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='It is as it should be - the great one has risen. My watch comes to an end...' WHERE entry=8286;
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc3='Has Anachronos returned?' WHERE entry=8286;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='This is very interesting information indeed, $N.  This sheds some light on the presence of the Twilight\'s Hammer in Silithus and will undoubtedly help us in our struggle against them.  Your efforts will be handsomely rewarded, $C.' WHERE entry=8287;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Could you be the first to earn favor among the Bronze Flight IN a thousand years?' WHERE entry=8288;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc3='You have proven your value to our efforts in Warsong Gulch. Continue to aid the cause and bring me more talismans of merit. Do this, and you will earn even more of our trust.',objectives_loc3='You obtained a Silverwing Talisman of Merit for your last task, talk to me again, and you gain your reward.',offerrewardtext_loc3='Thank you, $N. Your exploits in Warsong Gulch ring throughout Ashenvale Forest.' WHERE entry=8292;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc3='You have proven your value to our efforts in Warsong Gulch. Continue to rage against the Silverwing Sentinels! Bring me more marks of honor!',objectives_loc3='You obtained a Warsong Mark of Honor for your last task, talk to me again, and you gain your reward.',offerrewardtext_loc3='The night elves and their allies must tremble at even the whisper of your name! For the Horde!' WHERE entry=8293;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='<Captain Shatterskull roars in triumph.>$B$BHow much more can they withstand? How many more Alliance filth must perish at the hands of the Horde for them to retreat? Only time will tell, $R.' WHERE entry=8294;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='You got the resources! Great job! I\'ll send the resources to our quartermasters, who can quickly disperse them to our troops.$B$BThank you, $N. Indeed, performing successful missions like the one you achieved are how wars are truly won.' WHERE entry=8297;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Very good. I will get these to our quartermasters immediately, and a commendation for your actions will be sent to my superiors.$B$BOnce again, thank you $N. Your contributions to our struggles are noticed by footman and field marshal alike.' WHERE entry=8298;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Very good. I will get these to our quartermasters immediately, and a commendation for your actions will be sent to my superiors.$B$BOnce again, thank you $N. Your contributions to our struggles are noticed by grunt and high warlord alike.' WHERE entry=8300;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='You are not alone, hero. I will now grant you the ability to deputize others to help you IN your quest. If you are to be the champion of your people, you will need assistance IN your tasks and duties.' WHERE entry=8301;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Well done, hero. You will now be granted the ability to deputize another Agent of Nozdormu.' WHERE entry=8302;
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc3='Anachronos',offerrewardtext_loc3='You are the hope of Kalimdor, $N.' WHERE entry=8303;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='<Commander Mar\'alith lowers his head in contemplation.>$B$BWhether she is alive or dead, I must do what is right. She must be found. Alas, I am bound by duty to this outpost. Will you help me once more, $N?' WHERE entry=8304;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='You can feel a great sorrow revolving around this crystal. The force is so powerful that you feel as if you might collapse and die of sadness.' WHERE entry=8305;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='<Commander Mar\'alith clutches at his chest.>$B$BC\'Thun? WHAT is the meaning of all this? What is C\'Thun? How could this fiend have turned my sweet Natalia into the monster that you described?' WHERE entry=8306;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='This book contains several common recipes and a few unusual ones. After browsing through it for a few seconds you spot a recipe that involves sandworm meat.' WHERE entry=8307;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Well this explains a lot. If you ever find a way into Ahn\'Qiraj, keep an eye out for ol\' Brann. I\'m afraid that he\'ll be powerless without his monkey.' WHERE entry=8308;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='I can\'t make heads or tails of these glyphs. I\'ve never seen anything like it! I hope Frankal\'s research can shed some light on this mess.' WHERE entry=8309;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Outstanding! Don\'t wander off too far, kid. We might need you to take on another task or two.' WHERE entry=8310;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Wow, you got them all!  You\'re awesome!$B$BThank you for trick-or-treating for me.  Here, take these pumpkin treats - I think you\'ll like them a lot!$B$BHappy Hallow\'s End, $N!' WHERE entry=8311;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Wow, you got them all!  You\'re awesome!$B$BThank you for trick-or-treating for me.  Here, take these pumpkin treats - I think you\'ll like them a lot!$B$BHappy Hallow\'s End, $N!' WHERE entry=8312;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Let\'s have a look at that...$B$BThis seems simple enough.  They have their own names for some of the herbs, but those are simple enough to figure out.  Here, let me show you!' WHERE entry=8313;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='The reason the dwarves could not decipher the glyphs is because there is nothing to decipher. The shifting outer layer of the prism must properly align with the inner crystal\'s markings in order for the message to be transmitted. Clever...$B$BWhile we should be able to translate this data, we must first unlock the code. There is only one clue on the surface of the prism - assuming the rubbings were transferred correctly - and it looks grim.' WHERE entry=8314;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='I hold 20,000 years of history in my hands, $N!' WHERE entry=8315;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='War comes, $N, and with it comes untold horrors. You have done all that could be asked of you and for that you should be rewarded.$B$BShould this... this prophecy ever come to pass...$B$B<Geologist Larksbane turns pale.>$B$BThe future of us all could be at an end.$B$BThese armaments will prove invaluable to your campaign in this desert.' WHERE entry=8316;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Excellent! You\'re a life saver. These dumplings turned out to be quite good. Didn\'t really expect such good taste from the Twilight\'s Hammer.' WHERE entry=8317;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Excellent!  I\'ll stash these away, maybe they\'ll be useful later.' WHERE entry=8318;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Excellent work!  I\'ll put a good word in for you.' WHERE entry=8319;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='That was a task well performed, $N.  Your slaying of the Twilight geolords must have dealt a grievous blow to the cult.  Let us hope their plans are slowed...' WHERE entry=8320;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='You\'ve done it!  Vyral is killed!  This can only mean doom for the Twilight Hammer\'s operations in Silithus. There may be more of them scurrying about, but the blow you dealt to the cult today is one from which they will not easily recover.' WHERE entry=8321;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='The keg is filled with ale.$B$BHaving successfully fought your way inside the inn, you now place the eggs inside the keg. You can smell the foul odor permeating the air...' WHERE entry=8322;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Excellent!  I will get to decoding these as soon as possible.  If I find anything of interest I\'ll find some way to get the information to you.' WHERE entry=8323;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Excellent!  I can\'t wait to read these. Please do keep bringing the encrypted texts here if you find them.' WHERE entry=8324;
