UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Let us observe a minute of silence for our fallen mates, $N.$B$B<The Bloodsail Traitor grins at you and winks.>$B$BBeing a traitor is one thing, murdering yer own buckos... that\'d be just downright despicable, aye!' WHERE entry=9259;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Hmm. From what you\'ve told me, the voices within the circles... they must be used for communication of some kind. I shudder to think what unnatural minds are contacted through such magic. Regardless, you seem to have emerged whole and sane.  The Argent Dawn appreciates your service.' WHERE entry=9260;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Hmm. From what you\'ve told me, the voices within the circles... they must be used for communication of some kind. I shudder to think what unnatural minds are contacted through such magic. Regardless, you seem to have emerged whole and sane.  The Argent Dawn appreciates your service.' WHERE entry=9265;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Thank you, $N. You\'re on a quick path to redeeming yourself with our fair town.' WHERE entry=9266;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='I\'m happy you\'re seeing the error of your ways, $N. Keep the supplies coming; we\'re not going to forget about you so easily, $Gmister:miss;!' WHERE entry=9267;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Keep it coming, $N. Us goblins don\'t forget that easily!' WHERE entry=9268;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Yarrr... if ye be keen on enjoying the company of us experienced sea dogs, you\'d best belay dressing like a blaggard! Here, put on something proper \'fore I keelhaul yer hide.$B$BThese\'ll fit ye better than they ever fit that old dog, Red-Eyed Ben. Lost him in a devil of a storm at sea.$B$BWear \'em with pride, mate!' WHERE entry=9272;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Hm, you took this from the corpse of one of the invading abominations?$B$BWe have received word about the necropolis base camps that are being summoned by the Scourge. I suspect they wanted to create one inside Stormwind. It is good that they were unseccessful.' WHERE entry=9292;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='You have proven that you are not entirely useless, mortal.' WHERE entry=9319;
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc3='Have you found your way through the dark?' WHERE entry=9319;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Your spirit glows with the warmth of the Kalimdor fires, friend. Is the heat not invigorating? Once the power fades from you, perhaps these will help rekindle the feeling.' WHERE entry=9322;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Ah, here you are. A little wearier, a bit dustier, but enlightened! The heat touches us all during this season and unites us; your very being glows with the power of the fires you touched. Ah, but these days enlightenment is taken as a rather poor reward for being sent on a task, I suppose. Take these, then, and enjoy the celebration.' WHERE entry=9323;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='What\'s this? Unless I\'m mistaken, this flame has been taken from the heart of Orgrimmar itself! The fierce hearts of the orcs and trolls are reflected in its searing heat. What a fine addition to our collection--how brave you are, stealing into the enemy\'s lair to retrieve the sacred flame!' WHERE entry=9324;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Unless I miss my guess, this fire has been taken from the cliffs of Thunder Bluff! How it sings with the power of the spirits! You are quite the thief, $N. Take this as just payment for your skill. Now, if only we had the flames of all three cities...' WHERE entry=9325;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Hm... what a strange fire! It is subdued, nearly smoldering, but the heat is intense. And you received this from the Undercity, you say? Fascinating. With the flames of all three cities, who knows what we could accomplish?' WHERE entry=9326;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='And this brightly-burning fire... you say it came from Stormwind? Remarkable! That must have been quite an adventure! I\'ll pay you for this, of course. If you find anything else like this, be sure to speak with me again.' WHERE entry=9330;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='This hearty flame must be from the halls of Ironforge; it\'s as stalwart as the dwarves themselves. A fine catch, $N. If I had the fires of the other cities... ah, but never mind. Here is your payment.' WHERE entry=9331;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='This fire aches of ancient sorrow, $N. You pulled this from the roots of Teldrassil, you say? Fascinating! Here is a reward for your skill. Return to me should you find anything else like this; I may have a use for it.' WHERE entry=9332;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='You honor us, $N. With your continued efforts we will overcome all obstacles.' WHERE entry=9338;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='You\'ve proven yourself, today, $N.$B$BWhile I have little else to give you, I do have this crown; a fitting gift for a conqueror. May it light your way.' WHERE entry=9339;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='I must say, this shell has a strange aura. It seems only fitting that part of your reward for retrieving it would be to test its magical capabilities...' WHERE entry=9362;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Splendid! Splendid!$B$BNow we are able to reform this magic into a new spell. Behold!' WHERE entry=9364;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='You\'ve proven yourself, today, $N.$B$BWhile I have little else to give you, I do have this crown; a fitting gift for a conqueror. May it light your way.' WHERE entry=9365;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Excellent! It seems we\'ve appointed dutiful Flamekeepers this year if the bonfires are as well-kept as you claim. Thank you for inspecting them for me; here, take this as a small token of my esteem.' WHERE entry=9367;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Excellent work, $N. With the shadows destroyed, it can only be a matter of time before the Lich King decides to recall his necropolises and leave us in peace.' WHERE entry=9368;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='You have proven that you are not entirely useless, mortal.' WHERE entry=9386;
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc3='Have you found your way through the dark?' WHERE entry=9386;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Ahhh, so they do still burn. I am glad; it would not do for those fires to burn out before their time. You have done well, $N. Take this with my blessing.' WHERE entry=9388;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='So you\'ve returned, and you\'ve seen to the emerald flames of the continent. What do you think, mm? A rare and wonderful sight, to be certain. I am aware, however, that tangible rewards are better appreciated... so please, take this for your trouble.' WHERE entry=9389;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='The Alliance needs every able body they can get. The Horde has been receiving a steady supply of reinforcements from the northern part of the continent, and it\'s been a struggle to keep up.$B$BLet me explain the situation to you.' WHERE entry=9415;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='It\'s good that you\'re here, but there\'s no time to waste making small talk. You need instructions, and then you need to get out there.$B$BListen up.' WHERE entry=9416;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Thank the Light you were successful.$B$BNow if we could only have started this sooner, our need would not be so desperate. We must keep the bounty of the desert from falling into the hands of the Horde.' WHERE entry=9419;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='You\'ve done well, $N. These resources will be added to our stockpiles, and every bit is to our gain and our enemy\'s loss.' WHERE entry=9422;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc3='Very good, $N. It will be important for us to hold these towers against future attacks, and for that we may need your assistance until reinforcements can be brought in to secure the area.' WHERE entry=9664;
